A married woman shocked many people after giving a graphic details how she has been sleeping with her dad since she was 18 years old. While speaking on a show Tales from the Powder room hosted by Shirley E.F Tibilla aka Cookie Tee on GHOne TV, the young lady who is 34 years old and married with 2 children, revealed her father is the biological father of all her two children but her husband does not know any of that. She went on to explain that, her mother found out when she was 22 years old and died shortly after that. She has since had the death of her mother on her conscience. The young lady went on to explain that, all her past relationship failed because she was never satisfied with any of their sexual prowess; she always preferred her dad’s. She went on to recount how she sneaks from time to time to sleep with her father and her husband thinks they are just close because of her mother’s death. The purpose of the letter to Tales from the Powder room is to seek help on how to stop this act since she does not want to lose her husband. She also does not want to hurt her father either.